    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed status consistent with MRL 2 requirements for a Class II CPB device. The computational model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions within the assessed operating envelope.",
